                        <item name="Line" index="5" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">'assign a different action.</item>
                        <item name="Line" index="6" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">'The default implementation is to just return the line itself.</item>
                        <item name="Line" index="7" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">'If you return types that implement IGH_Goo, this component</item>
                        <item name="Line" index="8" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">'will work substantially faster.</item>
